INSPIRATIONS & CREDITS:

This project drew inspiration from the following open-source projects:

- WeakAuras2 (https://github.com/WeakAuras/WeakAuras2)
  License: GNU GPL v2
  The gold standard for WoW combat display frameworks. While WeakAuras is no
  longer functional in WoW 12.0 Midnight due to API restrictions, its design
  philosophy of customizable combat displays deeply influenced this addon.

- SenseiClassResourceBar (https://github.com/Snsei987/SenseiClassResourceBar)
  License: MIT
  A clean, modern resource bar addon for WoW 12.0. Its approach to
  LibEQOL integration, Settings API usage, and 12.0-compatible patterns
  served as a key reference for this addon's architecture.

- Arc UI (https://github.com/devdeadviz/arc-ui)
  License: Not specified
  A styling framework whose component-based design approach inspired
  the modular UI structure of badomeow.
